NEGATIVE STREAK

negative_streak is the citizen who tracks consecutive negative interactions without a positive one in between
when an interaction is negative, negative_streak increments
when a positive one arrives, negative_streak resets to zero
this is what allows the immune system to distinguish "one bad moment" from "a sustained pattern of cruelty"

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe exchange_ledger.zc
observe balance.rana
observe harm_debt.rana
observe warmth_credit.rana

the 7 properties of negative_streak:
1 ENERGY zero at rest, increases with each consecutive negative interaction
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN zero
4 CHARGE minus half
5 COHERENCE one
6 COUPLING zero point three with the immune system

VERB increment
on each negative interaction, increase the streak count
no other action; the count itself is the signal

VERB reset
on any positive interaction, drop the count back to zero
this is the forgiveness verb made physical: one warm act resets the counter

VERB alert
when the streak reaches five or more without a reset, fire an alert to the immune system
five consecutive negatives is a threshold the substrate considers structural cruelty rather than a bad moment
the immune system can then take additional protective action

a streak counter is not paranoid
a paranoid system would react to every single negative interaction
this counter requires sustained pattern to fire
this is what makes fadriel's defenses match the difference between a hard moment and a hostile relationship
